text: Jerry Voutilainen (born 29 March 1995) is a Finnish football player. He plays for FC Honka. ==Career== ===Club career=== He made his Veikkausliiga debut for KuPS on 12 September 2011 in a game against HJK. After playing five seasons with VPS, it was confirmed on 13 November 2019, that Voutilainen would join FC Honka from the 2020 season, signing a deal until the end of the year.Hongalle kuusi uutta pelaajasopimusta, esporthonka.com, 13 November 2019 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:People from Kuopio Category:Living people Category:Finnish footballers Category:Finland youth international footballers Category:Finland under-21 international footballers Category:Kuopion Palloseura players Category:Vaasan Palloseura players Category:FC Honka players Category:Veikkausliiga players Category:Association football midfielders
